import uuid

    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)
client.user.get_username(
    limit=0,
    id=uuid.UUID(
        "d5e9c84f-c2b2-4bf4-b4b0-7ffd7a9ffc32",
    ),
    date=datetime.date.fromisoformat(
        "2024-01-01",
    ),
    deadline=datetime.datetime.fromisoformat(
        "2024-01-01 00:00:00+00:00",
    ),

        name="string",
        tags=["string"],
